nitoring fabric will continue to play an increasingly critical role in bringing visibility to the application flows," said Merchant. "Gigamon is a leader in building traffic visibility systems. The versatility of Gigamon's platforms, its compelling vision and its strong team set it apart as an innovative leader in this space. I am excited to be part of the Gigamon team."




